4e04e4036f9b08f4bdec","tid":400385,"uid":12565,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在疑似插贓嫁禍、針對美國「911事件」的標語出現前不久，有「獨」派中人在美國白宮網站發起聯署，要求禁止內地學生赴美留學。標語出現後，立即有「港獨」分子呼籲美國駐港總領事館註銷內地學生簽證。三件事的發生時間如此「巧合」，容易令人聯想到由「獨」派一手策劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">以斷絕莘莘學子的追夢之路。</span></blockquote><br />\n我梗係斷絕你追夢之路啦<br />\n成班口講愛國<br />\n點知又借啲意嚟香港讀書搏容易啲去美國<br />\n讀兩三年搏搵工攞綠卡<br />\n一班漢奸走狗賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要追夢就同我乖乖地留係支那追支那夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb885b75f8542ae09d54027cf319ee2dea81c734","tid":400385,"uid":25494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:36:29.000Z","msg":"莘莘學子追夢之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eeb57a1365dd7f6cd150e66a8f0312a207899b","tid":400385,"uid":35370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T21:48:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又係大仆街寫嘅</span></span>"},{"pid":"84caa09f1eba16737a3392f0493b3a8f3545b4e1","tid":400385,"uid":44673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T22:39:39.000Z","msg":"本身可能無咩人知聯署單野。以家上埋報 間接宣傳，真係醒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59400c26d473fe8082e559a3932929e06b8179d0","tid":400385,"uid":39846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T22:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/GQzGdKHA6I9Uc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2FGQzGdKHA6I9Uc.gif&h=8ad3d9c6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">屌</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌</span>，屌你老母， 屌你老母，陳庭佳，陳庭佳"},{"pid":"4522eb3964f59658aa989c295af13a1188125728","tid":400385,"uid":98386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T22:59:37.000Z","msg":"支那咁好返支那讀啦 日日吹奏支那幾勁幾勁 升學應該首選支那大學"},{"pid":"cae60d39598d5228a9b89266a81af64e02282f3f","tid":400385,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:00:19.000Z","msg":"幫班後生共狗返歸建設中國都屌，即係文匯唔想見到中國富強啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f728e6328e0a2520d48f6149bad065bc027982","tid":400385,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:04:16.000Z","msg":"唔明有咩問題愛國先叫班子弟大陸讀 美國又危險，又講英文 係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbabc9904a390c51793a3444fa4f682f1b32717","tid":400385,"uid":11753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:05:57.000Z","msg":"中国人 美國夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d5abfdd400f31405a843c657747fe1243bc186","tid":400385,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bf473e8257affa638a5464b98a11f501af3931","tid":400385,"uid":2383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:12:23.000Z","msg":"移民共和國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490fbcad8ee1c7cf292298be3b9bdd523280d382","tid":400385,"uid":52943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:19:03.000Z","msg":"愛國莘莘學子做咩唔返支那讀書呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 